Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the night of the firework festival,\NKobayashi-sensei witnessed a murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up, just hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was a pawn shop owner, Sumida Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From those who may have held a grudge against\Nher, three suspects were found to have no alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, despite Kobayashi-sensei overhearing\Nquarreling between the culprit and the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was unable to select a voice that matched\Nthe bellowing from the recorded voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi-sensei was also acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, she seemed to be avoiding Inspector Shiratori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears she misunderstood his relationship with Detective Satou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To resolve the misunderstanding, Inspector\NShiratori visited our elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.19,0:00:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had met you long before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the girl who scolded the shoplifters in that bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was deeply moved by that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to join the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After seeing how brave you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry, but I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, about that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me â€” perhaps you mistook me for Detective Satou?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we continue lamenting the passing seasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be unable to confront the mysteries of cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,We're double solving the case and the love problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,And news about Kid has also flown in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,{\fscy120\fscx120\fad(100,0)\bord0.1}Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,{\fscy120\fscx120\fad(0,0)\bord0.1}The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,{\fscy120\fscx120\fad(0,50)\bord0.1}His name is: Detective {\t(1550,1551,\shad0\1c&H4331B1&)}Conan{\1c&H6AE8FA&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your precious trump card...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems to have gone to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you kept her hanging and\Ndidn't say anything until it was too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why'd you change the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you joined the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't because you saw Kobayashi-sensei stand up to the shoplifters...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wasn't it because you received the sakura\Ndecoration made from straw wrapper after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The sakura is the symbol of police officers in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Determined, kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a dignified flower of justice."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what Sensei said to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be better if I said I resolved to\Njoin the police after witnessing her bravery...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, upon hearing words like "brave" and "police"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She couldn't help but relate those to her look-alike Detective Satou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go clear it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't do you any good to make excuses now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't want to hear you speak, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is only one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can catch the culprit that Kobayashi-sensei saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And prove that Sensei's testimony was correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she'll open her heart to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, among those suspects, none of their\Nvoices matched the one Sensei heard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, she did tell us that she saw the\Nculprit's silhouette as they ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All she could tell was that the culprit had\Nbreasts and her long hair was tied back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, the moving truck with the large "{\c&HC8C8FF&}0{\r}" and\N"{\c&HC8C8FF&}9{\r}" printed on the side has yet to be located.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remind us who the suspects were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ex-leader of a ladies gang, the\Nfoul-mouthed Kagitani Kikuna-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A small restaurant manager who\Ncaught a cold, Takimoto Ryouko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the former hero of Koshien who injured his left shoulder and\Ncurrently works at a host club, Kodama Ryuusuke-san, these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as of now, based on Kobayashi-sensei's\Ntestimony, the culprit has not yet been identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, are you saying that Sensei was speaking nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi-sensei would never talk nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, all we have to do is deduce from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What made Sensei mistake the facts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was someone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:05:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspicious shadowy figure was watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that our culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the culprit saw Sensei's face after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit wouldn't know where to find her just by seeing her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet it was some camera brat who likes\Nto take candid photos of little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it won't do us any good to stay here, so let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi-sensei said she was staying late\Ntonight to prepare some teaching material.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So even if we wait, she won't be leaving anytime soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Teitan Elementary School.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm with the police, is Kobayashi-sensei there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have nothing else to say to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the truck with the {\c&HC8C8FF&}0{\r} and {\c&HC8C8FF&}9{\r} on the side has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We took some photos and were hoping you could identify them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you would please send them to me at a later date...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, the confirmation is needed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already asked the security guard to let me inside the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then come to the staff rooâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about the music room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I graduated from here and\Nused to be in the brass band club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It felt nostalgic when I looked around the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come to the music room then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great, I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's an old boy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder when he graduated?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were in the same class?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the music room was renovated last year, and\Nthe walls and desks have all been replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's there to be nostalgic about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, his voice just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prepare to brace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police HQ First Division, Criminal Investigation Section 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Assistant Inspector Satou Miwako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kodama Ryuusuke-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't a teacher!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was under Inspector Shiratori's care in the hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was switched out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're saying you knew I was going to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Based on Kobayashi-sensei's testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:10:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that "the culprit is a woman" and "I saw a truck with "{\c&HC8C8FF&}0{\r}" and "{\c&HC8C8FF&}9{\r}"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that all just nonsense spouted by that damned teacher!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She just thought she saw a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The silhouette of your elbow pressing on\Nyour injured shoulder while running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looked just like a woman's chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, because a female snatcher was lurking in that area...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder that she imagined the culprit to be a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman looked just like a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Sensei heard a man and woman arguing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then mistook the body she found as that of the man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would easily believe the culprit was the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that reasoning correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be hard to think the bellowing was really from the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you also cut your long hair to try to deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, what Sensei saw on the side of the truck at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't the numbers {\c&HC8C8FF&}0{\r} and {\c&HC8C8FF&}9{\r}, but the alphabet letters {\c&HC8C8FF&}O{\r} and {\c&HC8C8FF&}S{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of the {\c&HE2FFC7&}OSAKA NICO-NICO TRANSPORTATION{\r}\Ncompany had been painted on there in romaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The walls obscured them enough to look like numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That truck was hired to move the furniture of Agasa-san's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, we confirmed with the truck driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the fact that you and the victim were seen entering that alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more thing: as for you knowing Kobayashi-sensei\Nhappened to be an elementary school teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was because I yelled out "Sensei" as I arrived on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When a child calls someone "Sensei," the first thing\Nthat comes to mind is an elementary school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You searched the nearest elementary school to find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And aimed to silence her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to mess her up before she remembered anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And threaten her not to give any more testimonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I don't deserve to get thrown\Nin the slammer for killing that devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, didn't that "devil" loan you five million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It costs money to pursue one's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Medical bills for my shoulder, trainer fees...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite her looks, that woman was a high school baseball fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knew about me and had high hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, soon after she learned that my\Nshoulder was completely busted...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She changed her attitude with the flip\Nof her hand and treated me terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I still had a chance to become a\Nbatter, she demanded payment every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, she told me to bring my personal\Nseal and sign a life insurance policy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what the victim said about "Listen up, just hand it over" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was my seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was planning to take out a life\Ninsurance policy on me and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I killed her before she could do me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I could go on pursuing my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was self-defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Criminal Law, Article #36.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An act unavoidably performed to protect the\Nrights of oneself or any other person...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Against imminent and unlawful infringement is not punishable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An act exceeding the limits of self-defense\Nmay lead to the punishment being reduced...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or may exculpate the offender in light of the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are the provisions of self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time of the crime, you used a\Nbladed weapon with the intent to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So none of these circumstances apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, turning a bat which fulfills\Ndreams into a weapon to silence peopled...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earns you no right to talk about dreams at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Criminal Law, Article #235.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A person who steals the property of\Nanother commits the crime of theft...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And shall be punished by imprisonment for up to ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it really you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the bookstore back then!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you finally remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since long before these children were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sappy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she the teacher who gave Shiratori-kun butterflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I swear I've seen her face before...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's yours, yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you didn't know that when you two switched!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiratori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Care to join us for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'll have to pass this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet that's Kobayashi-sensei's homemade bento!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Homemade bento...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to make me a bento?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you... like... a bento...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna buy a bento at the store, get one for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can choose the style!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as it stuffs my belly, I'll like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The news about Kid this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sent out another notice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, his target is a big jewel owned by Suzuki Jirokichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kirin's Horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has plant seeds from tens of thousands of years ago mixed in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A valuable piece of amber!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that notice was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:16:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding the amber that was discovered at the old temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it just last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since they had it advertised on TV\Nand in newspapers every single day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even Kid would take the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do kirins have horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two small ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're talking about giraffes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kirin in question is said to be completely covered in golden scales...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is shaped like a deer, has a cow's tail and a horse's hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Growing from its dragon-like head is a single horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a divine beast from Chinese mythology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fscy80\fscx80}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hazure dragon\h\h\hwhite tiger\N{\r}Then, it's akin to Seiryuu and Byakko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you been summoned again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't heard anything yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it, Edogawa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're having another duel with Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have a strategy prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just Conan again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi and the others wanna duel with Kid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun's the one who chases Kid away every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I please have a word with the Detective Boys too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Care to share your enthusiasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advisor Suzuki Jiroukichi announced it at the press conference today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's seeking assistance from the entire Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Advisor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what to think about placing\Nchildren at the site of Kaitou Kid's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell from that guy's advance notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"On the night of the next full moon at 7:00 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll be paying a visit to receive Kirin's Hornâ€”Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"PS. This time, let us cease the child's play...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And engage in battle as adults."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How conceited, he revealed his own weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he says "as adults," he means not to invite children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means Kaitou Kid is weak against children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weak against children?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even a master of disguise like him can't appear as a short child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kids at the scene would only be a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then our strategy is\Nto invite an entire crowd of children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beyond that, the full moon he mentioned is two nights from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day that mountain temple will be directly hit by the typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The intense rain will prevent him from using his trademark hang glider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With his wings clipped, Kaitou Kid is nothing more than a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll lead the Detective Boys and make a\Ngrand arrest in front of the TV camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be a perfectly beautiful chapter to adorn my autobiography!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They suit you all so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those Detective Boys parkas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, allow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:12.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,Shinkai Juri (37)\NReporter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm a reporter, Shinkai Juri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:12.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:16.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And sitting next to me is my cameraman, Masui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:17.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,Masui Shougo (41)\NCameraman
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And sitting up front is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:27.44,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hisumi Isao (38)\NSoundman
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:27.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm the soundman, Hisumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I'd heard that the soundman was a young boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They couldn't get in contact with him,\Nso they called me at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that just because the typhoon's\Ncoming, he just chickened out like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That youngster...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really pouring now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How're the clothes I had made for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had these parkas made for us, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd look more like a detective group with matching clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We really like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is this Kirin's horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the looks of things, there's a big pillar in the middle....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the four corners are white, black...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Green, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red pedestals, that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Copper pedestals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The color paint flaked off and the top looks bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There seems to have been a statue here, but it's been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something like a keyhole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch things at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've warned the kids that the pedestals\Nhave a mild electrical current running through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kids only learn through pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll show you right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By using these white, black, red, and green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four keys I'm holding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori, I require the assistance of your subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure to turn off the current!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut off the power for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you use the colored keys on matching pedestals?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the sound of the electrical current in the pedestals being shut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After each beep...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The green, red, white, and black pedestals,\Nin that order, will cease to be electrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, your signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an1}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an3}What was that sound?\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Ah, that's...\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an1}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hOne, two-and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The central pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's splitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the Kirin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the yellow jewel on its head is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, must be the amber they call "Kirin's Horn."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, come get it if you dare, Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right here, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there was just one keyhole, I could guard it by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Ayumi and the others will guard them for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.83,0:24:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must mean that Kaitou Kid and any of his accomplices...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.84,0:24:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are still here, that's what!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.60,0:24:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sparrow
